WEBVTT

00:02:26.443 --> 00:02:30.657
Olimlar entomofagiya rivojlanayotgan
mamlakatlar uchun oziq-ovqat masalasida

00:02:30.681 --> 00:02:33.503
iqtisodiy jihatdan samarali
yechim bo'lishi mumkin deyishadi

00:02:33.527 --> 00:02:36.466
Hasharotlarda 80% gacha 
protein mavjud, va ular

00:02:36.490 --> 00:02:38.313
organizmning hayotiy muhim tarkibiy

00:02:38.337 --> 00:02:40.856
qismlari bo'lib, katta 
energiyaga ega yog', tola,

00:02:40.880 --> 00:02:44.264
vitaminlar va minerallar 
singari mikroelementlarga ega.

00:02:44.288 --> 00:02:47.228
Bilasizmi, ko'pchilik yeyish mumkin
bo'lgan hasharotlar tarkibi

00:02:47.252 --> 00:02:50.223
mol go'shti bilan bir xil miqdorda
yoki undan ko'proq mineral

00:02:50.247 --> 00:02:54.670
temir moddasiga ega. Temir tanqisligini
hozirgi kunda dunyodagi eng keng tarqalgan

00:02:54.694 --> 00:02:58.398
oziqlanish muammosi deb hisoblasak, 
ular ulkan, foydalanilmagan manba emasmi?

00:02:58.422 --> 00:03:00.555
Taom qurtlari yana bir to'yimli misoldir.